high_descs: Turn right and walk to the small wooden table near the chair across the room.
Pick up the blue credit card from the lower left corner of the table.
Turn around, hang a right at the coffee table and walk to the tall lamp in the corner to the right.
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Keep the fireplace to your left side and walk to the wooden table across from it.
Pick up the credit card from the wooden table.
Go to the left of the wooden table where the lamp is in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the credit card and turn the lamp on.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the table to the left of the couch.
Pick up the credit card that's on the left front corner of the table.
Move to the front of the lamp to the left of the table.
Look up at the lamp and turn it on.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a credit card and turn the lamp on.
